# Redis Configuration
# 
# RAILWAY DEPLOYMENT:
# Railway automatically provides Redis environment variables when you add a Redis service:
# - REDISHOST, REDISPORT, REDISUSER, REDISPASSWORD
# - OR REDIS_URL (both formats supported)
# No manual configuration needed - just add Redis service in Railway dashboard!

# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
# Start local Redis server: redis-server
# Then uncomment and configure:
# REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
# OR use individual settings:
# REDIS_HOST=localhost
# REDIS_PORT=6379
# REDIS_PASSWORD=your-redis-password

# Railway will automatically set PORT - don't change this
# PORT=8000